title: Crash on iOS simulator and device when trying to run Geth
body:
#### System information

Geth version: `1.6.2-unstable.9825`
OS & Version: OSX Sierra 10.12.4 / Xcode 8.3.2 (8E2002)
Commit hash : (if `develop`)

#### Expected behaviour
Starts node

#### Actual behaviour
crashes both on iOS simulator and device

#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour
Follow the iOS tutorial https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Mobile:-Account-management. Crashes every single time when running. Also tried to use the stable and develop versions, still the same issue.
